***
###
### Ethereum transactions are accepted into the contract's address and are registered.
### The manager of the lottery is the deploying account that controls the contract
### Only the manager can see the contract balance and select a random winner
### A user can send as much tx as they want to boost their winning chances
### The entirre balance will then be automatically transferred to the selected winner's address and the lottery is reset for the next round.
